[{"Code":"en","Title":"Installments","Slug":"installment","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"errorBox\" data-background=\"#f9e2e4\" data-border=\"#7e1115\" style=\"background:rgb(249, 226, 228);border-left:4px solid rgb(126, 17, 21);overflow:auto;\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">Placeholder for installments once available on payments api v3</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"6e1553c9-3671-4560-b094-2c789770b14e\" data-start=\"2177\" data-end=\"2297\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"></p><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Installments","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Installment","Slug":"installment","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">[OPTIONAL]</p><p data-block-id=\"09a2a4e8-987f-4e08-b299-06966458cf3e\">{{Product name}} is only available in {{country}}, {{country}}, and {{country}}.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">The first paragraph should be a brief summary of what will be covered in this article. Be straightforward. Mention only relevant points. Keep it concise, about 3-4 sentences.</p><p data-block-id=\"40dfd135-a242-4409-91a2-1e653153772b\">Use bullet points to list down features (if any).</p><ul data-block-id=\"65ad46c5-620c-44ce-a241-9864d10ff333\"><li data-block-id=\"3a502032-228e-46a3-853d-a976f7b5b944\"><p data-block-id=\"b28e870a-e819-4e36-baa3-fdd1839b3433\"><strong>Feature #1</strong> — description</p></li><li data-block-id=\"31728fce-427e-42a2-95d7-7db5efebcce4\"><p data-block-id=\"955769df-ef5e-4970-a1a7-2b935c10cbf1\"><strong>Feature #2</strong> — description</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0040ee89-b030-47a1-a940-31ff266caae9\"><p data-block-id=\"c0ba3757-b30f-4e41-ad82-453e3ca1623d\"><strong>Feature #3</strong> — description</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Write subsections in H2</h2><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">To add a table, click the + sign on the right side and select ‘Table’.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"708\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:708px;width:708px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">Title</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">Title</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">Title</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\">Row 1</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"b81a7bad-f451-4886-a7ee-62a6f3b236e0\">Row 2</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"a5a015f5-b58d-4808-ab02-d152803a94ad\">Row 3</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"85382ea1-2254-4987-be83-9856cbb06daa\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"f4791891-d660-4c70-8338-ebe394f0bb4a\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"ee04624c-463e-46c3-aa64-af6edb5e6e95\">Inserting media</h2><ol data-block-id=\"ad4fe56f-e803-42bd-9228-ae79256cabd2\"><li data-block-id=\"e8d5a759-0187-40fe-b8a6-8efa0d13feb1\"><p data-block-id=\"819e48ce-9a3c-496c-8ad3-4476c2b720e2\">Click the plus icon on the right to upload your image (you can also copy paste it)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5af2bcbb-c099-4668-ae22-186c0d3c9769\"><p data-block-id=\"08a0a742-fdcd-4c23-a159-7522bdbeabbd\">Once uploaded, select the image, then click <strong>Style </strong>&gt; <strong>Rounded</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"2e66b3ad-e910-4bca-a33b-f1aa9bf97d28\"><p data-block-id=\"eeca9763-917c-4076-8da1-f8293d4ff561\">You can also click <strong>Edit</strong> to highlight certain parts of the screen </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\"><img data-block-id=\"2ab1853e-5d2b-4d17-b220-65d1f5bfcfd5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(4).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(4).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"1f37857f-7456-443d-aca3-147afcbad375\">How to write instructions</h2><p data-block-id=\"385988f4-f224-4dee-9ef4-cc1b6724c27d\">Use numbered steps to write instructions. Highlight specific buttons in bold. No need to add punctuation at the end of each step. If you want to add images, add them after each line of text.</p><ol data-block-id=\"f472865b-728c-4d98-a65e-7f54fcc42df2\"><li data-block-id=\"a51375b4-10ff-4f5e-b4f0-ba5a7e29b79d\"><p data-block-id=\"bde2fe77-8994-454b-b794-e83ec089391a\">Click <strong>Balance</strong> &gt; <strong>Top Up</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"191f12ef-849e-46ad-bde8-15bfad31ea9d\"><p data-block-id=\"91805134-01ff-4d3b-9f57-d6fb611ff808\">Fill in your details</p><p data-block-id=\"741d3e85-dd80-4427-8ccd-1f564de660d5\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8da38e1b-e676-4773-93cc-2d86606aa137\"><img data-block-id=\"7a483302-90bb-417c-8f98-ac36c3c844f5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot%202024-09-12%20at%2015.50.05(1).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-12 at 15.50.05(1)\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"\"></p></li><li data-block-id=\"e5fdc74f-e5ca-4e12-8b4a-33319081a70e\"><p data-block-id=\"b9f26407-5d62-48ac-8990-66e30e8e4f7a\">Click <strong>Confirm</strong></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"b70ec001-6f86-480f-a525-adbb470fd118\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Installment","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Installment","Slug":"installment","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">[OPTIONAL]</p><p data-block-id=\"09a2a4e8-987f-4e08-b299-06966458cf3e\">{{Product name}} is only available in {{country}}, {{country}}, and {{country}}.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">The first paragraph should be a brief summary of what will be covered in this article. Be straightforward. Mention only relevant points. Keep it concise, about 3-4 sentences.</p><p data-block-id=\"40dfd135-a242-4409-91a2-1e653153772b\">Use bullet points to list down features (if any).</p><ul data-block-id=\"65ad46