ecific buttons in bold. No need to add punctuation at the end of each step. If you want to add images, add them after each line of text.</p><ol data-block-id=\"f472865b-728c-4d98-a65e-7f54fcc42df2\"><li data-block-id=\"a51375b4-10ff-4f5e-b4f0-ba5a7e29b79d\"><p data-block-id=\"bde2fe77-8994-454b-b794-e83ec089391a\">Click <strong>Balance</strong> &gt; <strong>Top Up</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"191f12ef-849e-46ad-bde8-15bfad31ea9d\"><p data-block-id=\"91805134-01ff-4d3b-9f57-d6fb611ff808\">Fill in your details</p><p data-block-id=\"741d3e85-dd80-4427-8ccd-1f564de660d5\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8da38e1b-e676-4773-93cc-2d86606aa137\"><img data-block-id=\"7a483302-90bb-417c-8f98-ac36c3c844f5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot%202024-09-12%20at%2015.50.05(1).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-12 at 15.50.05(1)\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"\"></p></li><li data-block-id=\"e5fdc74f-e5ca-4e12-8b4a-33319081a70e\"><p data-block-id=\"b9f26407-5d62-48ac-8990-66e30e8e4f7a\">Click <strong>Confirm</strong></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"b70ec001-6f86-480f-a525-adbb470fd118\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Installment","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Installment","Slug":"installment","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#f9e2e4;border-left:4px solid #7e1115;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"errorBox\" data-background=\"#f9e2e4\" data-border=\"#7e1115\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">Placeholder for installments once available on payments api v3</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"6e1553c9-3671-4560-b094-2c789770b14e\" data-